column26: Replace Amber Heard w/Actor MaKenzie Lauren in Aquaman2. Domestic Violence has NO Gender!
column33:
Replace Amber Heard from Aquaman 2 
with MaKenzie Lauren ❤️ Take a stand against D​omestic Violance.
column34:
Domestic Violence has NO GENDER!

Amber Heard is a ABSOLUTE DISGRACE to ALL SURVIVORS of DOMESTIC VIOLENCE!! 

Men are victims of domestic abuse, just like women. This must be recognized, and action must be taken to prevent a known abuser from being celebrated within the entertainment industry.

We need to take a stand and do what is right! Amber does Not deserve Any Screen time, Especially when Johnny had it all taken. Please Sign and Share this petition! Together our Voices will be Heard!!!

Let's make the Change and get this petition viral!!  Share with Friends and Family and on Social Media!!  Remember Sharing is caring!❤️

Makenzie is a Very Beautiful & Very Talented Actor!  MaKenzie is also a Published Children's Book Author a Model and a Mom to 3 Beautiful Children. MaKenzie Lauren would be Absolutely Perfect for the Character Mera for Aquaman2!!

*Take a peak at MaKenzie Lauren on Instagram 

 https://instagram.com/_makenzie.lauren_?igshid=YmMyMTA2M2Y=

Thank you!!!

column34:
Domestic Violence has NO GENDER!

Amber Heard is a ABSOLUTE DISGRACE to ALL SURVIVORS of DOMESTIC VIOLENCE!!

Let's make the Change and get this petition viral!!  Share with Friends and Family and on Social Media!!  Remember Sharing is caring!❤️

Makenzie is a Very Beautiful & Very Talented Actor!  MaKenzie is also a Published Children's Book Author a Model and a Mom to 3 Beautiful Children. MaKenzie Lauren would be Absolutely Perfect for the Character Mera for Aquaman2!!

*Take a peak at MaKenzie Lauren on Instagram 

 https://instagram.com/_makenzie.lauren_?igshid=YmMyMTA2M2Y=

Thank you!!!

*Take a peak at MaKenzie Lauren on Instagram

Thank you!!!

Amber Heard is a ABSOLUTE DISGRACE to ALL SURVIVORS of DOMESTIC VIOLENCE!! 

Men are victims of domestic abuse, just like women. This must be recognized, and action must be taken to prevent a known abuser from being celebrated within the entertainment industry.

Let's make the Change and get this petition viral!!  Share with Friends and Family and on Social Media!!  Remember Sharing is caring!❤️

Makenzie is a Very Beautiful & Very Talented Actor!  MaKenzie is also a Published Children's Book Author a Model and a Mom to 3 Beautiful Children. MaKenzie Lauren would be Absolutely Perfect for the Character Mera for Aquaman2!!

*Take a peak at MaKenzie Lauren on Instagram 

 https://instagram.com/_makenzie.lauren_?igshid=YmMyMTA2M2Y=

Thank you!!!

column34:
Domestic Violence has NO GENDER!

Amber Heard is a ABSOLUTE DISGRACE to ALL SURVIVORS of DOMESTIC VIOLENCE!! 

Men are victims of domestic abuse, just like women. This must be recognized, and action must be taken to prevent a known abuser from being celebrated within the entertainment industry.

We need to take a stand and do what is right! Amber does Not deserve Any Screen time, Especially when Johnny had it all taken. Please Sign and Share this petition! Together our Voices will be Heard!!!

Let's make the Change and get this petition viral!!  Share with Friends and Family and on Social Media!!  Remember Sharing is caring!❤️

Makenzie is a Very Beautiful & Very Talented Actor!  MaKenzie is also a Published Children's Book Author a Model and a Mom to 3 Beautiful Children. MaKenzie Lauren would be Absolutely Perfect for the Character Mera for Aquaman2!!

*Take a peak at MaKenzie Lauren on Instagram 

 https://instagram.com/_makenzie.lauren_?igshid=YmMyMTA2M2Y=

Thank you!!!
